---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import CareerJourney from '../components/CareerJourney.jsx';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About Dr. Hamidah — 30 Years Transforming Malaysian Schools"
  description="Career journey of Dr. Hamidah Che Abdul Hamid: from English teacher to headteacher of Malaysia's High-Performance Schools. BA English Literature, Master TESL, PhD Educational Leadership."
>
  <!-- Page Header -->
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-navy-900 to-navy-800 text-white py-16">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <p class="text-gold-400 font-medium text-sm uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">Career Journey</p>
      <h1 class="font-serif text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold mb-4">About Dr. Hamidah</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-navy-200 max-w-2xl">Three decades in Malaysian education — from classroom teacher to leading a school of 1,700.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Bio Section -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <!-- Headshot -->
      <div class="flex justify-center mb-10">
        <div class="w-36 h-36 rounded-full overflow-hidden border-4 border-gold-400 shadow-lg">
          <img src="/images/hamidah-headshot.jpg" alt="Dr. Hamidah Che Abdul Hamid" class="w-full h-full object-cover" width="400" height="400" loading="eager" />
        </div>
      </div>
      <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold text-navy-900 mb-6">The Story</h2>
      <div class="prose prose-navy max-w-none space-y-4 text-navy-700 leading-relaxed">
        <p>
          Hamidah's career started in 1995 as an English teacher in Kelantan's primary schools. Before teaching, she completed a Diploma in Banking Studies at UiTM — giving her an operational mindset that would later set her apart in school&nbsp;management.
        </p>
        <p>
          After nine years in the classroom, she moved into administration as Senior Assistant, spending a decade overseeing curriculum, teacher development, and school operations. She earned her BA in English Literature (UPM) and Master in TESL (UiTM) — all while working&nbsp;full-time.
        </p>
        <p>
          In 2014, she was appointed Headteacher. Over four schools in 12 years, she consistently raised the bar: winning national awards, tripling exam results, championing digital transformation, and building communities around&nbsp;education.
        </p>
        <p>
          Her PhD at UniSZA formalised what she'd been practising all along — resilient leadership. She didn't just study it. She lived it at every school she&nbsp;led.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Career Timeline -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-navy-50">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold text-navy-900 mb-10 text-center">Career Timeline</h2>
      <CareerJourney client:visible />
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Education -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold text-navy-900 mb-8">Education</h2>
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-gold-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-gold-600" aria-hidden="true" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M21.42 10.922a1 1 0 0 0-.019-1.838L12.83 5.18a2 2 0 0 0-1.66 0L2.6 9.08a1 1 0 0 0 0 1.832l8.57 3.908a2 2 0 0 0 1.66 0z"/><path d="M22 10v6"/><path d="M6 12.5V16a6 3 0 0 0 12 0v-3.5"/></svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-navy-900">PhD — Educational Leadership</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-navy-500">Universiti Sultan Zainal Abidin (UniSZA) · Viva passed Dec 2025</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-navy-600 mt-1">Thesis: "Development of Mathematical Formulation of Resilient Leadership Index for Head Teachers' Leadership Model"</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-navy-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-navy-600" aria-hidden="true" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 6.042A8.967 8.967 0 006 3.75c-1.052 0-2.062.18-3 .512v14.25A8.987 8.987 0 016 18c2.305 0 4.408.867 6 2.292m0-14.25a8.966 8.966 0 016-2.292c1.052 0 2.062.18 3 .512v14.25A8.987 8.987 0 0018 18a8.967 8.967 0 00-6 2.292m0-14.25v14.25"/></svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-navy-900">Master of Education (TESL)</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-navy-500">Universiti Teknologi MARA (UiTM) · 2007 – 2011</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-navy-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-navy-600" aria-hidden="true" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M2 3h6a4 4 0 0 1 4 4v14a3 3 0 0 0-3-3H2z"/><path d="M22 3h-6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v14a3 3 0 0 1 3-3h7z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-navy-900">BA English Literature</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-navy-500">Universiti Putra Malaysia (UPM) · 2000 – 2004</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-navy-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-navy-600" aria-hidden="true" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M3 3v18h18"/><path d="m19 9-5 5-4-4-3 3"/></svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-navy-900">Diploma in Banking Studies</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-navy-500">Universiti Teknologi MARA (UiTM) · 1985 – 1989</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-navy-600 mt-1">Business foundation before pivoting to education</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Skills & Languages -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-navy-50">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold text-navy-900 mb-8">Skills & Competencies</h2>
      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-navy-900 mb-3">Languages</h3>
          <div class="space-y-2">
            <div>
              <div class="flex justify-between text-sm mb-1"><span class="text-navy-700">Bahasa Malaysia</span><span class="text-navy-500">Native</span></div>
              <div class="h-2 bg-navy-200 rounded-full"><div class="h-2 bg-navy-700 rounded-full w-full"></div></div>
            </div>
            <div>
              <div class="flex justify-between text-sm mb-1"><span class="text-navy-700">English</span><span class="text-navy-500">Professional (BA + Master)</span></div>
              <div class="h-2 bg-navy-200 rounded-full"><div class="h-2 bg-navy-700 rounded-full w-[90%]"></div></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-navy-900 mb-3">Digital Skills</h3>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
            <span class="bg-white text-navy-700 text-xs font-medium px-3 py-1 rounded-full border border-navy-200">Google Certified Educator L1</span>
            <span class="bg-white text-navy-700 text-xs font-medium px-3 py-1 rounded-full border border-navy-200">Microsoft 365</span>
            <span class="bg-white text-navy-700 text-xs font-medium px-3 py-1 rounded-full border border-navy-200">Google Workspace</span>
            <span class="bg-white text-navy-700 text-xs font-medium px-3 py-1 rounded-full border border-navy-200">Canva</span>
            <span class="bg-white text-navy-700 text-xs font-medium px-3 py-1 rounded-full border border-navy-200">Zoom / Teams</span>
            <span class="bg-white text-navy-700 text-xs font-medium px-3 py-1 rounded-full border border-navy-200">ChatGPT / AI Tools</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-navy-900 text-white text-center">
    <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-4">
      <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Interested in Working Together?</h2>
      <p class="text-navy-200 mb-8">Available for leadership roles in private education from March&nbsp;2026.</p>
      <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 bg-gold-500 hover:bg-gold-600 text-navy-900 font-bold rounded-lg transition-[background-color,box-shadow] duration-200 focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-gold-500 focus-visible:ring-offset-2 hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-gold-500/25">
        Get in Touch →
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
